%20citizenship%20in%20the%20South%20Pacific%20Ocean%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20fugitive%20is%20wanted%20in%20India%20for%20alleged%20financial%20irregularities.%20Earlier%2C%20Lalit%20Modi%20filed%20an%20application%20with%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission%20in%20London%20to%20surrender%20his%20Indian%20passport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVanuatu%20Prime%20Minister%20Jotham%20Napat%20has%20asked%20the%20country's%20Citizenship%20Commission%20to%20cancel%20the%20passport%20issued%20to%20Lalit%20Modi%20%26quot%3Bfollowing%20recent%20revelations%20in%20international%20media%26quot%3B%2C%20his%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20all%20standard%20background%20checks%2C%20including%20Interpol%20screenings%2C%20conducted%20during%20his%20application%20showed%20no%20criminal%20convictions%2C%20I%20have%20been%20made%20aware%20in%20the%20past%2024%20hours%20that%20Interpol%20twice%20rejected%20Indian%20authorities'%20requests%20to%20issue%20an%20alert%20notice%20on%20Mr%20Modi%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20substantive%20judicial%20evidence.%20Any%20such%20alert%20would%20have%20triggered%20an%20automatic%20rejection%20of%20Mr%20Modi's%20citizenship%20application%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Napat%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20emphasised%20that%20holding%20a%20Vanuatu%20passport%20is%20a%20privilege%2C%20not%20a%20right%2C%20and%20applicants%20must%20seek%20citizenship%20for%20legitimate%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNone%20of%20those%20legitimate%20reasons%20include%20attempting%20to%20avoid%20extradition%2C%20which%20the%20recent%20facts%20brought%20to%20light%20clearly%20indicate%20was%20Mr%20Modi's%20intention%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20added%20that%20the%20Vanuatu%20government%20has%20significantly%20strengthened%20the%20due%20diligence%20aspect%20of%20its%20citizenship%20by%20investment%20Programme%20over%20the%20past%20four%20years.%20This%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20office%20s