.%20and%20proceeds%20with%20the%20second%20phase%20according%20to%20the%20agreed-upon%20terms%2C%26quot%3B%20spokesman%20Hazem%20Qassem%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas's%20key%20demands%20for%20the%20second%20phase%20include%20a%20hostage-prisoner%20exchange%2C%20Israel's%20complete%20withdrawal%20from%20Gaza%2C%20a%20permanent%20ceasefire%2C%20border%20crossings%20reopening%20and%20lifting%20the%20blockade%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20United%20States%20president%20Joe%20Biden%20had%20also%20outlined%20a%20second%20phase%20involving%20the%20release%20of%20remaining%20living%20hostages%2C%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20all%20Israeli%20forces%20left%20in%20Gaza%2C%20and%20establishment%20of%20a%20permanent%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20meeting%20mediators%2C%20another%20Hamas%20spokesman%2C%20Abdel%20Latif%20al-Qanoua%2C%20said%20indicators%20were%20so%20far%20%26quot%3Bpositive%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20office%20said%20it%20would%20send%20delegates%20to%20Doha%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20truce%20largely%20halted%20more%20than%2015%20months%20of%20fighting%20in%20Gaza%2C%20where%20virtually%20the%20entire%20population%20was%20displaced%20by%20Israel's%20relentless%20military%20campaign%20in%20response%20to%20the%20October%207%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six-week%20first%20phase%20led%20to%20the%20exchange%20of%2025%20living%20Israeli%20hostages%20and%20eight%20bodies%20for%20the%20release%20of%20about%201%2C800%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20held%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20allowed%20in%20much-needed%20food%2C%20shelter%20and%20medical%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Israel%20cut%20off%20the%20aid%20flow%2C%20UN%20rights%20experts%20accused%20the%20government%20of%20%26quot%3Bweaponising%20starvation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20UN%20distribution%20of%20flour%20in%20Jabalia%2C%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20Abu%20Mahmoud%20Salman%2