18827727.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Controversy%20Over%20CT%20Final%20Presentation%20Event.%20Pak%20Great%20Asks%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20No...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20is%20being%20strongly%20criticised%20for%20not%20sending%20a%20single%20representative%20to%20the%20final%20of%20the%202025%20Champions%20Trophy%20at%20the%20Dubai%20International%20Stadium%20on%20Sunday.%20As%20India%20won%20the%20title%20after%20beating%20New%20Zealand%20by%20four%20wickets%20in%20the%20final%2C%20the%20podium%20was%20shared%20by%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20chairman%20Jay%20Shah%2C%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20president%20Roger%20Binny%20and%20secretary%20Devajit%20Saikia%20and%20New%20Zealand%20Cricket%20(NZC)%20director%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Roger%20Twose%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F420-roger-twose-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERoger%20Twose%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20present%20accolades%20to%20players.%20PCB%20chief%20operating%20officer%20Sumair%20Ahmed%2C%20also%20the%20tournament%20director%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20was%20in%20Dubai%20but%20was%20not%20invited%20to%20the%20podium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Telecom%20Asia%20Sport%20(www.telecomasia.net)%2C%20PCB%20chairman%20Mohsin%20Naqvi%20did%20not%20travel%20to%20Dubai%20due%20to%20his%20official%20commitment%20as%20the%20country's%20interior%20minister.%20Mohsin%20had%20conveyed%20to%20the%20ICC%20that%20he%20was%20busy%20in%20the%20joint%20parliament%20session%20in%20Islamabad%2C%20where%20President%20Asif%20Zardari%20was%20due%20to%20address%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20fast%20bowler%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shoaib%20Akhtar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F381-shoaib-akhtar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShoaib%20Akhtar%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20to%20social%20media%20and%20said%20Pakistan%20not%20sending%20a%20single%20representative%20on%20a%20stage%20is%20%26quot%3Bbeyond%20his%20understanding%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20won%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%20today%20but%20I%20noticed%20something%20strange.%20Pakistan%20were%20the%20hosts%20in%20the%20tournament%20but%20there%20were%20no%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20representatives%20here%20(at%20the%20trophy%20presentation).%20This%20is%20beyond%20my%20understanding.%20Why%20was%20there%20no%20one%20to%20represent%20us%20and%20give%20the%20trophy%3F%20Please%20think%20about%20it%2C%20it's%20a%20world%20stage%20but%20sadly%20I%20could%20not%20see%20any%20PCB%20members.%20Feeling%20very%20down%20to%20see%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Akhtar%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20literally%20beyond%20my%20understanding.%3Cbr%3E%5CnHow%20can%20this%20be%20done%3F%3F%3F%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Fchampionstrophy2025%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23championstrophy2025%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FCPIUgevFj9%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FCPIUgevFj9%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Shoaib%20Akhtar%20(%40shoaib100mph)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fshoaib100mph%2Fstatus%2F1898786882562957599%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%209%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20former%20Pakistan%20players%20believe%20a%20wrong%20reflection%20will%20be%20conveyed%20to%20India%20that%20the%20PCB%20chairman%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20ceremony%20because%20India%20had%20reached%20the%20final%20and%20also%20became%20the%20ultimate%20winner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202025%20Champions%20Trophy%20was%20Pakistan's%20first%20home%20tournament%20in%2029%20years%20but%20the%20hosts%20were%20embarrassingly%20eliminated%20in%20the%2