0with%20dizzying%20tariff%20actions%20that%20have%20veered%20in%20various%20directions%20since%20he%20took%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelivering%20a%20farewell%20address%20to%20party%20supporters%20at%20a%20hall%20in%20Ottawa%20before%20his%20successor%20was%20announced%2C%20Trudeau%20said%20%26quot%3BCanadians%20face%20from%20our%20neighbor%20an%20existential%20challenge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Most%20serious%20crisis'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20party%20meeting%2C%20Carney%20supporter%20Lozminda%20Longkines%20told%20AFP%20that%20Trump's%20repeated%20musings%20about%20making%20Canada%20the%2051st%20US%20state%20were%20%26quot%3Ba%20blessing%20in%20disguise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20so%20united...%20We%20have%20a%20common%20enemy%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2071-year-old%20said%20before%20the%20results%20were%20announced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGreg%20MacEachern%2C%20who%20declined%20to%20say%20who%20he%20supported%2C%20agreed%20the%20party%20would%20emerge%20from%20the%20vote%20tightly%20focused%20on%20Trump.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20serious%20time%2C%20and%20I%20think%20people%20have%20taken%20this%20leadership%20race%20very%2C%20very%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20MacEachern%2C%20wearing%20a%20hockey%20jersey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarney%20has%20argued%20that%20he%20is%20the%20ideal%20counter%20to%20Trump's%20disruptions%2C%20reminding%20voters%20that%20he%20led%20the%20Bank%20of%20Canada%20through%20the%202008-2009%20financial%20crisis%20and%20steered%20the%20Bank%20of%20England%20through%20the%20turbulence%20that%20followed%20the%202016%20Brexit%20vote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20released%20from%20the%20Angus%20Reid%20polling%20firm%20on%20Wednesday%20shows%20Canadians%20see%20Carney%20as%20the%20favorite%20choice%20to%20face%20off%20against%20Trump%2C%20potentially%20offering%20the%20Liberals%20a%20boost%20over%20the%20opposition%20Conservatives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%