ily%20in%20Orlando%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20drive%20to%20Celebration%20to%20explore%20the%20community%2029%20years%20after%20the%20first%20families%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20my%20trip%2C%20I%20also%20spoke%20with%20Joe%20Davison%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20postmen%20in%20Celebration.%20He%20began%20working%20at%20its%20post%20office%20in%201996%20and%20retired%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20trade%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Davison%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20was%20by%20far%20the%20best%2013%20years%20of%20work%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20spoke%20with%20Celebration%20HOA%20President%20Don%20McDonald%2C%20who%20has%20lived%20there%20with%20his%20family%20since%20the%20mid-1990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20few%20years%20it%20was%20very%20tight%20knit%2C%26quot%3B%20McDonald%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%20only%20a%20hundred%20and%20some%20odd%20houses.%20We%20knew%20everybody%20and%20the%20kids%20knew%20everybody%2C%20and%20we%20felt%20relatively%20safe%20letting%20the%20kids%20run%20free%20and%20free%20range.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDisney%20broke%20ground%20in%201994.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224204%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Homes%20in%20Celebration%2C%20Florida%2C%20under%20construction%20in%201996.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ad04b66630eb10385c6ff0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222820%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECelebration%20under%20construction%20in%20the%20mid-1990s.%3Cp%3Emark%20peterson%2FCorbis%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Celebration%20Company%20%E2%80%94%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20The%20Walt%20Disney%20Company%20%E2%80%94%20developed%20the%20community%20with%20the%20help%20of%20several%20architects%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobert-stern-why-architects-should-draw-no-computer-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERobert%20A.M.%20Stern%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Stern's%20firm%20helped%20create%20the%20master%20plan%2C%20which%20sought%20to%20build%20a%20picturesque%20landscape%20endowed%20with%20small-town%20charm%20and%20Southern%20flair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20emphasis%20on%20tree-lined%20streets%2C%20parks%2C%20and%20civic%20buildings%20will%20create%20a%20strong%20public%20realm%2C%20an%20essential%20ingredient%20to%20any%20real%20town%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ramsa.com%2Fprojects%2Fproject%2Fcelebration%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommunity%20is%20the%20main%20focus%20in%20Celebration%2C%20so%20the%20architects%20created%20their%20designs%20to%20encourage%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGarages%20are%20located%20on%20alleys%2C%20opening%20the%20streets%20to%20views%20of%20houses%20rather%20than%20garage%20doors%2C%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%20allowing%20for%20narrower%20lots%20which%20decrease%20walking%20distances%20and%20enhance%20the%20sense%20of%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20website%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20arrived%20on%20a%20balmy%20Saturday%2C%20the%20community%20appeared%20especially%20lively.%20A%20group%20of%20children%20performed%20a%20choreographed%20dance%20in%20a%20nearby%20park%2C%20where%20a%20cultural%20festival%20with%20booths%20representing%20different%20countries%20and%20a%20bouncy%20house%20was%20in%20full%20swing.%20Nearby%2C%20families%20strolled%20leisurely%20through%20the%20town%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDisney%20hosted%20a%20lottery%20to%20choose%20Celebration's%20first%20residents.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Houses%20in%20Celebration%2C%20Florida%2C%20in%202002.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ad05c87bb3f854015cb277%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222704%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHomes%20in%20Celebration%2C%20Florida%2C%20in%202002.%3Cp%3EJeff%20Greenberg%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECelebration's%20first%20residents%20scored%20their%20homes%20and%20apartments%20through%20a%20lottery%20hosted%20by%20The%20Walt%20Disney%20Company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%201995%20article%20from%20The%20Orlando%20Sentinel%20reported%20that%20once%20potential%20homeowners%20were%20chosen%2C%20they%20made%20a%20refundable%20%241%2C000%20deposit%20and%20an%20appointment%20with%20a%20sales%20consultant.%20The%20paper%20reported%20at%20the%20time%20that%20homes%20were%20worth%20between%20%24127%2C000%20to%20over%20%24500%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald%20and%20his%20family%20were%20among%20those%20who%20entered%20Disney's%20lottery.%20He%20and%20his%20wife%20wanted%20to%20live%20in%20Celebration%20for%20education%20options%20for%20their%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDisney%20was%20going%20to%20build%20a%20state-of-the-art%20school%2C%20so%20we%20wanted%20to%20get%20the%20kids%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20McDonald%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20residents%20began%20moving%20moved%20into%20Celebration%20in%201996%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20a%20bustling%20town%20just%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20moved%20there%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%2C%20but%20we%20weren't%20really%20that%20busy%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20Davison%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20in%20the%20post%20office%20during%20Celebration's%20early%20years%20allowed%20Davison%20to%20meet%20many%20of%20the%20new%20faces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20point%20in%20time%2C%20the%20post%20office%20was%20pretty%20slow%2C%20so%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20coming%20in%20were%20residents%2C%26quot%3B%20Davison%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20atmosphere%20among%20residents%20in%20Celebration%20was%20welcoming%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20different%20from%20his%20previous%20post%20office%20job%20in%20South%20Miami.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20them%20would%20let%20you%20know%20you%20didn't%20live%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Davison%20said%20about%20Miami.%20%26quot%3BIn%20Celebration%2C%20nobody%20ever%20treated%20me%20like%20an%20outsider%2C%20which%20is%20nice%20in%20that%20respect.%20You%20felt%20like%20part%20of%20the%20community.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%202%2C700%20people%20called%20Celebration%20home%20by%202000%2C%20according%20to%20the%20census%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESome%20modern%20Celebration%20homes%20cost%20millions.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Homes%20in%20Celebration%2C%20Florida%2C%20in%20February%202025.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ad06b47bb3f854015cb2c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EResidential%20homes%20in%20Celebration%2C%20Florida%2C%20in%202025.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Edmonds%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECelebration%20has%20grown%20quite%20a%20bit%20since%20the%20first%20residents%20arrived%20in%201996.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20neighborhood%20%E2%80%94%20or%20village%20%E2%80%94%20expansions%20were%20completed%20from%202000%20to%202003.%20The%20most%20recent%20expansion%20happened%20in%202021%20with%20Island%20Village%2C%20which%20is%20nestled%20into%20the%20west%20side%20of%20Celebration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20way%20to%20the%20town%20center%2C%20I%20noticed%20the%20idyllic%2C%20charming%20homes%20dotting%20the%20neighborhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHome%20prices%20in%20Celebration%20vary%2C%20but%20active%20property%20listings%20shared%20by%20local%20real%20estate%20agencies%20show%20a%20mix%20of%20six-%20and%20seven-figure%20residences.%20One%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc21carioti.com%2Flisting%2FFL%2FCelebration%2F416-Arbor-Circle-34747%2F203121605%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esix-bedroom%2C%20six-bathroom%3C%2Fa%3E%20home%20in%20Celebration%20Village%20is%20selling%20for%20%242.5%20million%2C%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2