et%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emy%20son%20was%20tearful%20or%20noisy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20only%20an%20endless%20stream%20of%20adoring%20aunties%20ready%20to%20help%20the%20moment%20they%20were%20needed%20%E2%80%94%20even%20before%20they%20were%20asked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2279865475-73df-4414-b72e-8339488645fa%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20a%20helicopter%20mom%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20former%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhelicopter-parenting-could-hurt-kids-2016-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehelicopter%20mom%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20this%20was%20new%20for%20me.%20Parenting%20in%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Bay%20area%20had%20been%20a%20notably%20solo%20venture%2C%20especially%20as%20a%20young%20mom%20whose%20friends%20weren't%20very%20interested%20in%20kids%2C%20let%20alone%20starting%20families.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20settled%20into%20our%20new%20home%20in%20Loei%20with%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsafest-countries-in-world-for-expats-living-abroad-ranking-work-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esmall%20community%20of%20expats%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20I%20learned%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20Thai%20people's%20friendliness%20and%20camaraderie.%20I%20enlisted%20the%20help%20of%20a%20nanny%20named%20Ot%2C%20who%20insisted%20we%20call%20her%20Auntie%20with%20the%20familiar%20Pa%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebefore%20her%20name.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPa%20Ot%20became%20a%20true%20auntie%20to%20my%20son%20and%2C%20frankly%2C%20like%20a%20second%20mother%20to%20me.%20With%20several%20kids%20of%20her%20own%20and%20much%20more%20experience%20than%20I%20had%2C%20she%20showed%20me%20how%20to%20soothe%20my%20baby's%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmosquito-bi