0we've%20always%20been%20in%20awe%20with%20what%20they%20can%20do%2C%20the%20limited%20number%20of%20players%20in%20the%20talent%20pool%2C%20but%20they%20just%20execute%20plans%20so%20well%2C%20they%20keep%20playing%20the%20kind%20of%20cricket%20that%20keeps%20them%20very%20much%20in%20the%20game.%20They're%20always%20been%20attacking%20and%20supportive%20of%20the%20bowlers%2C%20Credit%20to%20them%2C%20easily%20the%20best%20fielding%20unit%2C%20sad%20to%20see%20a%20very%20good%20friend%20of%20mine%20to%20be%20on%20the%20losing%20side%20(on%20Kane%20Williamson)%2C%20but%20they're%20always%20so%20good%20and%20they%20keep%20doing%20the%20basics%20well.%20That's%20what%20makes%20them%20such%20a%20competitive%20unit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741547820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F2qva4cs_virat-kohli-rohit-sharma_625x300_09_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fwhen-you-leave-virat-kohlis-huge-statement-amid-retirement-buzz-after-indias-ct-2025-triumph-7886169%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20saw%20a%20great%20buzz%20about%20the%20future%20of%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20in%20international%20cricket%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fwhen-you-leave-virat-kohlis-huge-statement-amid-retirement-buzz-after-indias-ct-2025-triumph-7886169%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20Breaks%20Silence%20On%20Retirement%20After%20Leading%20India%20To%20CT%202025%20Title%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20put%20to%20rest%20all%20speculations%20about%20his%20future%20in%20the%20ODI%20format%20after%20India%20won%20the%20Cha