ack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20makes%20him%20stand%20out%20at%20any%20gathering%20of%20leaders%20and%20emphasises%20that%20his%20country%20is%20fighting%20a%20war.%20His%20team%20has%20followed%20his%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20the%20Oval%20Office%20meeting%2C%20a%20reporter%20for%20a%20right-wing%20broadcaster%2C%20Brian%20Glenn%2C%20mockingly%20asked%20Zelensky%20why%20he%20was%20not%20wearing%20a%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20wear%20(a%20suit)%20after%20this%20war%20finishes%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelensky%20answered%20wearily%20in%20an%20exchange%20widely%20shared%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedia%20outlet%20Axios%20reported%2C%20citing%20sources%2C%20that%20Trump%20was%20irritated%20Zelensky%20did%20not%20wear%20a%20suit%20at%20the%20meeting%20after%20US%20advisers%20told%20him%20it%20would%20be%20more%20%26quot%3Brespectful%26quot%3B%20to%20wear%20a%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20remarked%20sarcastically%20when%20Zelensky%20appeared%20that%20%26quot%3Bhe%20is%20all%20dressed%20up%20today%26quot%3B%2C%20before%20virulently%20laying%20into%20the%20Ukrainian%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKremlin%20spokesman%20Dmitry%20Peskov%20gave%20a%20lengthy%20commentary%20on%20the%20Oval%20Office%20talks%20to%20state%20television%20on%20Sunday%2C%20expressing%20horror%20at%20the%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBeing%20a%20diplomat%20by%20profession%2C%20I%20could%20not%20believe%20my%20eyes%2C%20nor%20my%20ears%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20claiming%20that%20rulers%20have%20not%20resorted%20to%20such%20brutal%20tactics%20since%20%26quot%3Bancient%20times%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20used%20to%20happen%20in%20ancient%20times%2C%20that%20they%20would%20chop%20off%20the%20head%20of%20a%20state%20who%20went%20somewhere%20on%20a%20visit%20or%20put%20him%20in%20prison.%20But%20I%20think%20that%20even%20by%20the%20mediaeval%20era%2C%20that%20did%20not%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%