deal%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-countries-american-expats-live-work-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20expats%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20want%20to%20visit%20family%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20apartment%20was%20miles%20from%20the%20beach%2C%20but%20an%20inexpensive%20bus%20ride%20made%20getting%20there%20a%20snap.%20However%2C%20once%20we%20got%20to%20the%20miles%20of%20public%20beaches%2C%20we%20were%20disappointed%20to%20find%20very%20few%20designated%20access%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20harder%20to%20enter%20the%20beach%20than%20we%20expected%2C%20especially%20since%20we'd%20been%20used%20to%20walking%20from%20an%20oceanfront%20hotel%20directly%20onto%20the%20sand%20when%20we'd%20stayed%20in%20Canc%C3%BAn%20as%20tourists.%20This%20was%20definitely%20a%20drawback%2C%20but%20not%20an%20insurmountable%20one.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20though%2C%20we%20were%20pleasantly%20surprised%20at%20how%20similar%20downtown%20Canc%C3%BAn%20felt%20to%20our%20current%20neighborhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226bc30e78-d083-41ca-a5b1-2ddd25ed8637%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlaya%20del%20Carmen%20seemed%20to%20offer%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds%20for%20American%20expats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224804%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20view%20of%20water%20by%20Playa%20del%20Carmen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c71ec6b8b41a9673f99ad8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPlaya%20del%20Carmen%20has%20beaches%2C%20businesses%2C%20shops%2C%20and%20more.%20%3Cp%3EArturo%20Pe%C3%B1a%20Romano%20Medina%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELocated%20about%20an%20hour%20south%20of%20Canc%C3%BAn%20is%20the%20coastal%20town%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmexico-all-inclusive-resort-family-disappointed-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPlaya%20Del%20Carmen%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Unlike%20Canc%C3%BAn%2C%20Playa%20del%20Carmen%20doesn't%20have%20an%20isolated%20hotel%20zone%20separate%20from%20its%20residential%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20city%20has%20beaches%2C%20the%20famous%205th%20Avenue%20a%20couple%20of%20blocks%20away%2C%20and%20then%20local%20housing%20and%20businesses%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20major%20highway%20that%20runs%20from%20Canc%C3%BAn%20past%20Tulum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20liked%20that%20nearby%20neighborhoods%20could%20easily%20access%20the%20beach%20and%20popular%20spots%20like%205th%20Avenue.%20The%20lively%20area%20felt%20like%20Mexico's%20version%20of%20Bourbon%20Street%20in%20New%20Orleans%2C%20filled%20with%20tourists%2C%20vendors%2C%20and%20live%20music.%20This%20was%20fun%2C%20though%20I%20worried%20it%20could%20eventually%20be%20annoying%20to%20navigate%20while%20trying%20to%20do%20chores%20and%20run%20errands%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20the%20area%20felt%20overflowing%20with%20outstanding%20food%20and%20shopping%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20local%20offerings%2C%20we%20found%20popular%20American%20chains%20like%20Walmart%2C%20Sam's%20Club%2C%20Office%20Depot%2C%20and%20many%20familiar%20chain%20restaurants%20in%20the%20area%20that%20US%20expats%20missing%20home%20would%20surely%20enjoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Playa%20del%20Carmen%20doesn't%20have%20its%20own%20international%20airport%2C%20the%20one%20in%20Canc%C3%BAn%20is%20only%20about%20an%20hour%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2296d6bee7-86b6-46c1-8fe9-69efeb0d986b%5C%22%3EOverall%2C%20we%20can%20see%20why%20retirees%20would%20choose%20either%20place%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20exciting%20to%20see%20what%20else%20is%20out%20there%20for%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-us-to-mexico-in-50s-to-retire-comfortably-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmericans%20looking%20to%20retire%20abroad%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20appreciated%20how%20Playa%20del%20Carmen%20and%20Canc%C3%BAn%20both%20felt%20beautiful%20and%20walkable%2C%20with%20fairly%20easy%20access%20to%20airports%2C%20which%20is%20great%20for%20retirees%20moving%20away%20from%20family.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20can%20definitely%20understand%20why%20the%20warm%20weather%2C%20beaches%2C%20and%20other%20perks%20would%20bring%20expats%20to%20either%20place.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20we%20also%20realized%20the%20area's%20generally%20hotter%20temperatures%20weren't%20quite%20an%20ideal%20fit%20for%20us.%20For%20now%2C%20we%20still%20call%20Cuenca%20home.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpopular-american-retirement-destinations-mexico-cancun-playa-del-carmen-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741530901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c7202ab8b41a9673f99b20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpopular-american-retirement-destinations-mexico-cancun-playa-del-carmen-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20retirees%20abroad%2C%20we%20visited%20popular%20retirement%20destinations%20for%20Americans%20in%20Mexico%3A%20Canc%C3%BAn%20and%20Playa%20del%20Carmen.%20It's%20clear%20why%20many%20move%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Cynthia%20Staton%2CEdd%20Staton)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A78%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpopular-american-retirement-destinations-mexico-cancun-playa-del-carmen-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHouses%20With%204-5%20Bodies%20In%20Them%26quot%3B%3A%20Terrified%20Alawites%20In%20Syria%20Flee%20Attacks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20two%20days%2C%20Rihab%20Kamel%20and%20her%20family%20hid%20terrified%20in%20their%20bathroom%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Baniyas%20as%20armed%20men%20stormed%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20pursuing%20members%20of%20Syria's%20Alawite%20minority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coastal%20city%20is%20part%20of%20Syria's%20Alawite%20heartland%20that%20has%20been%20gripped%20by%20the%20fiercest%20violence%20since%20former%20president%20Bashar%20al-Assad%20was%20toppled%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20turned%20off%20the%20lights%20and%20hid.%20When%20we%20were%20able%20to%20flee%20our%20neighbourhood%20of%20Al-Qusour%2C%20we%20found%20the%20roads%20full%20of%20corpses%2C%26quot%3B%20Kamel%2C%20a%2035-year-old%20mother%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Christian%20family%20sheltered%20them%20and%20then%20helped%20them%20reach%20the%20frontier%20with%20Lebanon%2C%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20planned%20to%20flee%20across%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20crime%20did%20the%20children%20commit%3F%20Are%20they%20also%20supporters%20of%20the%20(toppled)%20regime%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20as%20Alawites%20are%20innocent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20erupted%20on%20Thursday%20after%20gunmen%20loyal%20to%20Assad%20attacked%20Syria's%20new%20security%20forces.%20The%20ensuing%20clashes%20resulted%20in%20dozens%20of%20deaths%20on%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWar%20monitor%20the%20Syrian%20Observatory%20for%20Human%20Rights%20later%20reported%20that%20security%20forces%20and%20allied%20groups%20killed%20at%20least%20745%20Alawite%20civilians%20in%20Latakia%20and%20Tartus%20provinces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterim%20President%20Ahmed%20al-Sharaa%2C%20who%20led%20the%20Islamist%20group%20Hayat%20Tahrir%20al-Sham%20that%20spearheaded%20the%20lightning%20offensive%20that%20toppled%20Assad%2C%20on%20Sunday%20called%20for%20%26quot%3Bnational%20unity%20(and)%20civil%20peace%26quot%3B%20to%20be%20preserved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGod%20willing%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20live%20together%20in%20this%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20mosque%20in%20Damascus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20villages%20and%20towns%20on%20the%20coast%2C%20people%20spoke%20of%20systematic%20killings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Minutes'%20from%20death%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssad%2C%20himself%20an%20Alawite%2C%20sought%20to%20present%20himself%20as%20protector%20of%20Syria's%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20authorities%20have%20repeatedly%20promised%20an%20inclusive%20transition%20that%20protects%20the%20rights%20of%20religious%20minorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Alawite%20heartland%20has%20nonetheless%20been%20gripped%20by%20a%20fear%20of%20reprisals%20over%20the%20Assad%20clan's%20decades%20of%20brutal%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaniyas%20resident%20Samir%20Haidar%2C%2067%2C%20told%20AFP%20two%20of%20his%20brothers%20and%20his%20nephew%20were%20killed%20by%20%26quot%3Barmed%20groups%26quot%3B%20that%20entered%20people's%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20an%20Alawite%20himself%2C%20Haidar%20belonged%20to%20the%20leftist%20opposition%20under%20the%20Assads%20and%20was%20imprisoned%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20began%20hearing%20explosions%20and%20gunfire%20on%20Friday%20morning%20with%20the%20arrival%20of%20forces%20deployed%20to%20the%20city%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Bforeigners%20among%20them%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20entered%20the%20building%20and%20killed%20my%20only%20neighbour%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20managed%20to%20escape%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20children%20to%20a%20Sunni%20neighbourhood%2C%20but%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20had%20been%20five%20minutes%20late%2C%20I%20would%20have%20been%20killed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20same%20day%2C%20armed%20men%20entered%20his%20brother's%20building%20100%20metres%20(yards)%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20gathered%20all%20the%20men%20on%20the%20roof%20and%20opened%20fire%20on%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Haidar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20nephew%20survived%20because%20he%20hid%2C%20but%20my%20brother%20was%20killed%20along%20with%20all%20the%20men%20in%20the%20building.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20another%20brother%2C%20who%20was%2074%2C%20and%20nephew%20were%20killed%20along%20with%20all%20the%20men%20in%20their%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20houses%20with%20four%20or%20five%20dead%20bodies%20in%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Haidar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20appealed%20to%20be%20able%20to%20bury%20our%20dead%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20has%20so%20far%20been%20unable%20to%20bury%20his%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Bodies%20in%20the%20sea'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20port%20city%20of%20Latakia%2C%20AFP%20heard%20testimonies%20from%20residents%20who%20said%20armed%20groups%20abducted%20a%20number%20of%20Alawites%20who%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20them%20was%20the%20head%20of%20a%20state-run%20cultural%20centre%2C%20Yasser%20Sabbouh%2C%20who%20was%20kidnapped%20and%20whose%20corpse%20was%20dumped%20outside%20his%20home%2C%20an%20AFP%20reporter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jableh%20further%20south%2C%20a%20resident%20spoke%20to%20AFP%20in%20tears%2C%20saying%20they%20were%20being%20terrorised%20by%20armed%20groups%20who%20had%20taken%20control%20of%20the%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20six%20of%20us%20in%20the%20house%2C%20with%20my%20parents%20and%20my%20brothers.%20There's%20been%20no%20electricity%20for%20four%20days%2C%20no%20water.%20We%20have%20nothing%20to%20eat%20and%20we%20do%20not%20dare%20go%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20fearing%20for%20his%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20than%2050%20people%20from%20among%20my%20family%20and%20friends%20have%20been%20killed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThey%20gathered%20bodies%20with%20bulldozers%20and%20buried%20them%20in%20mass%20graves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaafar%20Ali%2C%20a%2032-year-old%20Alawite%20from%20the%20region%2C%20fled%20to%20neighbouring%20Lebanon%20with%20his%20brother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20I'm%20going%20back%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20refugees%20without%20a%20homeland.%20We%20want%20countries%20to%20open%20up%20(channels%20for)%20humanitarian%20migration%20for%20Alawites.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741530840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fnf02im7_syria-afp-_625x300_09_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhouses-with-4-5-bodies-in-them-terrified-alawites-in-syria-flee-attacks-7885298%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20two%20days%2C%20Rihab%20Kamel%20and%20her%20family%20hid%20terrified%20in%20their%20bathroom%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Baniyas%20as%20armed%20men%20stormed%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20pursuing%20members%20of%20Syria's%20Alawite%20minority.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhouses-with-4-5-bodies-in-them-terrified-alawites-in-syria-flee-attacks-7885298%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Secret%20Service%20shoots%20armed%20man%20outside%20White%20House%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741530636000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F113f%2Flive%2F65e90cd0-fcef-11ef-b945-3d5d40c655bc.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc4gdwde82ldo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Donald%20Trump%20was%20not%20in%20the%20White%20House%20at%20the%20time.%22%2C%22autho