22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enursing%20homes.%3C%2Fa%3E%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ahcancal.org%2FAdvocacy%2FIssueBriefs%2FAHCA%2520Access%2520to%2520Care%2520Report%25202024%2520FINAL.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20over%20400%20nursing%20homes%20conducted%20by%20the%20American%20Health%20Care%20Association%20found%20that%2072%25%20had%20fewer%20employees%20in%202024%20than%20they%20did%20prior%20to%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20also%20showed%20that%2057%25%20of%20nursing%20homes%20said%20they%20had%20a%20waiting%20list%2C%2046%25%20said%20they%20began%20to%20limit%20their%20intake%20of%20residents%2C%20and%207%25%20said%20they%20were%20turning%20away%20patients%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20have%20right%20now%2C%20nor%20will%20we%20unfortunately%20ever%20have%20enough%20people%20who%20are%20trained%2C%26quot%3B%20Morrison%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20evidenced%20by%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20it%20takes%20for%20an%20appointment%20within%20our%20geriatric%20practices.%20It's%20evidenced%20by%20the%20number%20of%20older%20adults%20that%20need%20to%20be%20taken%20into%20the%20hospital%20that%20the%20inpatient%20services%20don't%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20see.%20And%20it's%20just%20the%20tip%20of%20the%20iceberg.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2210c338e0-da71-4bed-b5f4-6c91d0a7cec4%5C%22%3EA%20dwindling%20medical%20profession%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGurwitz%20says%20he%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20geriatrician%2C%20but%20the%20sentiment%20is%20rare%20among%20medical%20professionals.%20Data%20from%20the%20National%20Resident%20Matching%20Program%20showed%20that%20only%20174%20out%20of%20419%20available%20positions%20in%20geriatric%20specialty%20programs%20were%20filled%20in%202023%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20most%20unfilled%20programs%20the%20organization%20tracks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FLWshE%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Unfilled%20residency%20programs%20per%20specialty%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22185%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EConvincing%20people%20to%20specialize%20in%20the%20field%20isn't%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%2C%20the%20profession%20doesn't%20pay%20as%20much%20as%20some%20specializations.%20According%20to%20data%20from%20Salary.com%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.salary.com%2Fresearch%2Fsalary%2Fbenchmark%2Fphysician-geriatrics-salary%2Fnew-york-ny%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedian%20salary%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20geriatric%20physician%20in%20New%20York%20hovered%20around%20%24264%2C163.%20That's%20less%20than%20half%20the%20median%20salary%20of%20a%20cardiologist%20in%20New%20York%2C%20which%20stood%20at%20%24573%2C498%20a%20year%20as%20of%20March%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FjFmmp%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22214%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20perception%20that%20geriatrics%20medicine%20is%20a%20less%20distinguishing%20field%20than%20other%20areas%2C%20Gurwitz%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20are%20certain%20fields%20of%20medicine%20that%20are%20more%20prestigious%20in%20which%20they%20are%20more%20respected%20than%20others.%20Geriatrics%2C%20for%20one%20reason%20or%20another%2C%20is%20not%20among%20those%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarrell%20said%20he%20thinks%20that%20the%20complexity%20of%20treating%20older%20patients%20could%20be%20another%20factor%20turning%20professionals%20away%20from%20the%20trade.%20Geriatricians%20treat%20older%20adults%20who%20typically%20have%20overlapping%20health%20conditions%2C%20with%20some%20patients%20taking%20as%20many%20as%2020%20medications%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20prevent%20falls%3F%20How%20do%20you%20manage%20multiple%20chronic%20conditions%20for%20the%20same%20person%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20there's%20people%20in%20primary%20care%20who%20have%20more%20or%20less%20comfort%20with%20the%20complexity%20taking%20care%20of%20complicated%2C%20older%20adults%2C%20and%20that's%20what%20geriatrician%20is%20trained%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeriatric-care-aging-population-boomers-healthcare-nursing-homes-doctor-shortage-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741521601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670d35c36ac7b701e7cad25a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeriatric-care-aging-population-boomers-healthcare-nursing-homes-doctor-shortage-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%2C%20geriatric%20care%20experts%20told%20BI%20it's%20been%20hard%20attracting%20new%20doctors%20to%20the%20field.%20It's%20a%20problem%20for%20an%20aging%20US%20population.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40businessinsider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeriatric-care-aging-population-boomers-healthcare-nursing-homes-doctor-shortage-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Darjeeling%E2%80%99s%20Toy%20Train%20Has%20Chugged%20Through%20the%20Himalayas%20Since%201881%20%E2%80%94%20Here%E2%80%99s%20Why%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20UNESCO%20Icon!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDarjeeling%20has%20become%20synonymous%20with%20three%20things