alwood%2C%20and%20an%20astonishing%20variety%20of%20fruits%2C%20medicinal%2C%20and%20flowering%20trees%20from%20around%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Olives%20from%20Italy%20and%20Spain%2C%20Australian%20avocados%2C%20and%20Mexican%20dates%20have%20all%20found%20a%20home%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20adds%20mystique%20to%20this%20endeavour%20is%20the%20trial%20and%20success%20of%20growing%20saffron%20in%20such%20a%20hot%20climate.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20arrival%20of%20500%20saffron%20flowers%20in%202023%20was%20an%20unforeseen%20triumph%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20sustenance%2C%20the%20forest%20serves%20a%20purpose%20of%20community%20and%20conservation%2C%20not%20relying%20on%20fertilisers%20or%20pesticides%20but%20embracing%20natural%20farming%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20once-barren%20Keshar%20Parvat%20is%20now%20alive%20with%20the%20rustling%20of%20leaves%20and%20the%20chirping%20of%20birds.%20Wildlife%20has%20also%20returned%3B%20jackals%2C%20wild%20pigs%2C%20and%20over%2030%20bird%20species%20now%20roam%20freely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fkesar-parvat-1-1741002385.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wildlife%20and%20birds%20have%20returned%20in%20the%20once-barren%20Keshar%20Parvat.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fkesar-parvat-1-1741002385.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fkesar-parvat-1-1741002385-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fkesar-parvat-1-1741002385-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fkesar-parvat-1-1741002385-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fkesar-parvat-1-1741002385-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-410974%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWildlife%20and%20birds%20have%20returned%20to%20the%20once-barren%20Keshar%20Parvat.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20initial%20stages%20to%20cultivate%20this%20ecosystem%20were%20fraught%20with%20adversity.%20Dr%20Garg%20had%20drilled%20three%20borewells%20to%20arrange%20for%20a%20water%20source%20to%20water%20his%20saplings%2C%20but%20he%20found%20them%20all%20dry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUndeterred%2C%20he%20resorted%20to%20purchasing%20water%20through%20tankers%2C%20an%20exhaustive%20and%20expensive%20process.%20%E2%80%9CEach%20tanker%20of%206%2C000%20litres%20cost%20me%20about%20Rs%20600%20in%20normal%20days%20and%20Rs%202%2C000%20in%20summer.%20At%20least%20one%20water%20tanker%20was%20required%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20years%20later%2C%20the%20water%20table%20in%20surrounding%20areas%2C%20once%20considered%20hopeless%2C%20has%20risen%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20forest%E2%80%99s%20influence%20on%20local%20water%20cycles.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20did%20not%20get%20water%20even%20after%20digging%20borewells%20as%20deep%20as%20600%20feet.%20Now%2C%20I%20get%20water%20in%20the%20surrounding%20plain%20areas%20at%20just%20250%20feet.%20Now%2C%20I%20am%20not%20dependent%20on%20water%20tankers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20forest%20continues%20to%20mature%2C%20Dr%20Garg%20envisions%20its%20fragrant%20blossoms%20and%20vibrant%20foliage%20spreading%20joy%20and%20awareness%20far%20beyond%20the%20hill%20itself.%20His%20efforts%20extend%20an%20open%20invitation%20to%20anyone%20inspired%20to%20turn%20dreams%20into%20reality%2C%20even%20if%20it%20means%20being%20called%20%E2%80%98crazy%E2%80%99%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20readers%2C%20he%20has%20just%20one%20simple%20message%3A%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20should%20at%20least%20plant%20one%20tree%20in%20their%20lifetime.%20While%20you%20may%20think%20you%20are%20only%20planting%20a%20tree%2C%20it%20will%20give%20you%20and%20others%20fresh%20air%2C%20food%2C%20and%20shelter%2C%20boost%20the%20economy%2C%20and%20prevent%20disasters%20like%20floods%2C%20drought%20and%20landslides%20for%20decades%20to%20come.%20So%2C%20can%20we%20take%20care%20of%20at%20least%20one%20plant%20in%20our%20life%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20are%20inspired%20to%20join%20Dr%20Garg%20in%20his%20mission%20of%20tree%20plantation%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20him%20at%209425056228.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Megha%20Chowdhury%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Dr%20Shankar%20Lal%20Garg%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741354234000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2Fkesar-parvat-3-1741002510.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D410969%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%202019%2C%20a%20devastating%20fire%20destroyed%201%2C000%20trees%20in%20Dr%20Shankar%20Lal%20Garg%E2%80%99s%20forest%2C%20built%20on%20barren%20land.%20Despite%20the%20setback%2C%20his%20resilience%20turned%20dreams%20into%20reality.%20Today%2C%20Keshar%20Parvat%2C%20a%2022-acre%20lush%20forest%2C%20thrives%20with%20over%2040%2C000%20trees%2C%20showcasing%20the%20transformative%20power%20of%20determination%20and%20nature.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A51%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F410969%2Fretirement-teacher-turns-barren-hill-thriving-forest-madhya-pradesh%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Beyond%20Financial%20Aid%3A%20The%20Programme%20Helping%2095%25%20of%20Students%20Step%20into%20Careers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20Cybage%3C%2