%20about%20donating%20excess%20food%20instead%20of%20wasting%20it%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20of%20collecting%20and%20distributing%20food%20is%20well-organised.%20When%20a%20donor%20has%20excess%20food%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20from%20a%20corporate%20event%2C%20wedding%2C%20or%20any%20other%20occasion%2C%20they%20call%20the%20No%20Food%20Waste%20helpline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20team%20is%20dispatched%20with%20a%20vehicle%20to%20collect%20the%20food%2C%20which%20is%20then%20transported%20to%20the%20community%20kitchen.%20Once%20there%2C%20the%20food%20is%20checked%20for%20safety%2C%20properly%20packed%2C%20and%20distributed%20to%20shelters%20across%20the%20city.%20Our%20organisation%20works%20with%20a%20number%20of%20shelter%20homes%2C%20including%20Tower%20NGO%2C%20Regina%20Charitable%20Trust%2C%20and%20Integrated%20Women%20Development%20Institute%2C%20ensuring%20that%20food%20reaches%20those%20who%20need%20it%20the%20most%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Arun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaintaining%20hygiene%20and%20food%20safety%20rules%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20take%20extra%20care%20to%20make%20sure%20the%20food%20is%20not%20expired%20and%20eliminate%20any%20items%20that%20may%20cause%20allergic%20reactions.%20Hygiene%20is%20of%20utmost%20importance%2C%20so%20we%20ensure%20that%20everyone%20handling%20food%20wears%20gloves%2C%20and%20we%20maintain%20proper%20cleanliness%20in%20our%20kitchens.%20We%20always%20aim%20to%20serve%20warm%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F203341%2Ffree-food-atm-odisha-sambalpur-municipal-corporation-swaichha-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euntouched%20food%20to%20those%20in%20need%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20a%20dedicated%20team%20is%20responsible%20for%20overseeing%20these%20processes%20to%20make%20sure%20everything%20is%20done%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arun%20expla