0Godrej%20was%20founded%20in%201897%20to%20help%20build%20economic%20independence%20for%20India.%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20growing%20and%20strengthening%20this%20legacy%20of%20innovation%20for%20a%20cause%2C%20building%20for%20a%20more%20sustainable%20future%20while%20placing%20our%20planet%20and%20people%20alongside%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGIG%20houses%20several%20rapidly%20growing%20businesses%20that%20are%20the%20leaders%20in%20their%20respective%20categories.%20Godrej%20Consumer%20Products%20(GCPL)%20is%20an%20emerging%20markets%20FMCG%20leader%20in%20Home%20and%20Personal%20Care%2C%20with%20a%20growing%20presence%20in%20Asia%2C%20Africa%20and%20Latin%20America.%20Godrej%20Properties%20(GPL)%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20leading%20real%20estate%20developer%20by%20sales%20and%20brings%20the%20Godrej%20philosophy%20of%20innovation%2C%20sustainability%2C%20and%20excellence%20to%20the%20real%20estate%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGodrej%20Agrovet%E2%80%99s%20(GAVL)%20portfolio%20businesses%20address%20key%20challenges%20faced%20by%20Indian%20agriculture%2C%20improving%20the%20productivity%20of%20Indian%20farmers%20through%20innovative%20products%20and%20services%20that%20sustainably%20increase%20crop%20and%20livestock%20yields.%20Godrej%20Industries%20(Chemicals)%2C%20the%20group%E2%80%99s%20oldest%20business%2C%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20leading%20manufacturer%20of%20oleochemicals%20and%20surfactants.%20Godrej%20Fund%20Management%20(GFM)%20is%20the%20real%20estate%20private%20equity%20arm%20of%20the%20group.%20Godrej%20Capital%20(GC)%2C%20the%20newest%20company%20in%20the%20group%2C%20is%20a%20fast-growing%20financial%20services%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20more%20information%20on%20the%20Company%2C%20please%20log%20on%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.godrejindustries.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewww.godrejindustries.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publish