ink%20about%20suitable%20solutions.%20%E2%80%9CLiving%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20a%20detachable%20stroller%20for%20my%20twins%20that%20was%20compact%20enough%20to%20fit%20in%20narrow%20spaces%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2040-year-old%20mother%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%20thing%20I%20realised%20was%20that%20twin%20parenting%20is%20different%20from%20single%20parenting.%20For%20instance%2C%20many%20people%20advise%20parents%20to%20sleep%20when%20the%20baby%20sleeps%2C%20but%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20feasible%20for%20twin%20parents%2C%20as%20they%20rarely%20sleep%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20The%20second%20challenge%20is%20the%20struggle%20with%20exclusive%20breastfeeding%20for%20twins.%20Most%20twin%20mothers%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20milk%20supply%20to%20nourish%20both%20babies%2C%20and%20even%20if%20they%20do%2C%20the%20process%20of%20breastfeeding%20two%20babies%20is%20physically%20and%20emotionally%20draining.%20This%20often%20leads%20to%20twin%20mothers%20experiencing%20postpartum%20blues%20or%20even%20depression%20due%20to%20the%20overwhelming%20demands.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20they%20need%20support%20from%20fellow%20twin%20parents%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-21-at-09.30.06-4_11zon-1740921702-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20twin%20stroller%20by%20TwinsTribe%20is%20their%20star%20product%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-21-at-09.30.06-4_11zon-1740921702-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-21-at-09.30.06-4_11zon-1740921702-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebette